 </svg>Carbon Footprint Reduction</h4>
 <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">A single GaN charger operating at 95% efficiency vs 85% efficiency saves approximately 15-20W of wasted energy per charger. For a business deploying 10,000 chargers, this translates to substantial aggregate energy savings and reduced carbon emissions over the product lifecycle.</p>
 </div>
 <div class="bg-green-50 rounded-xl p-6">
 <h4 class="font-black text-green-700 uppercase mb-3"><svg class="icon-bolt mr-2" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" viewBox="0 0 448 512">
